1. git remote -v //查看远程库

<alias>  <link>

2.git remote add <alias>  <link>  // set the alias of link_remote_repos

3.git push <alias> <branch name>
or
git push <link> <branch name> //push the local_repos to the remote_repos_files 

4.git pull <alias> <branch> //pull the remote_repos_files to the local_repos

=================================== be invited by others collaborator =============

open the <invited_link> given by others

5.git clone <link of the repos>  // get the remote_repos to the local

do the 3 or 4 or edit your own version
